metadata.name: notturno generativo #106
metadata.description:
by fabiello.art

my first generative nft is a nocturnal landscape written in p5.js, where I present my personal fusion of code and figurative art, a vision of hills and trees under a sky of stars and a full moon.
Each iteration presents a number of random variables such as to make the possible night scenarios tend to infinity, each capable of evoking different emotions due to its colors and shapes.

I like to imagine how every possible landscape is somehow connected to a physical or metaphysical place of the personal experience of the beholder. 
The use of the machine and the code, of human thought and its evolution up to our time, as an instrument of discovery and imaginative exploration of territories of the body and the soul.

The code of the trees is derived from J. Poliachik's Generative Trees.
1080x1080 px 
_

https://twitter.com/fabielloart

metadata.name: enter the dragon #11
metadata.description:
This generative token uses a modified fractal algorithm based on the Dragon Curve.
https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dragon_curve

Random colours and radius are used to visualize the pattern.


color scheme: 14 variations of sets of 4 colours
start angle: first direction, between 0 and 90
loops: how many iterations to pre-compute, between 7 and 15
angle: the angle of each turn, between 85 and 90
frames: total number of frames before the animation stops. Between 2500 and 5000.
alpha: alpha value used for some transparency. Between 200 and 250.

metadata.name: tiredEyes #11
metadata.description:
tired eyes
try to pull me away
but they are just weak little goo balls
with no say so

while homunculus puppeteers

- strings pulled
- fate sealed
- stage set

"the show just started.
youre not leaving."

ok. one more hour.
but thats it.


created with hydra (https://hydra.ojack.xyz/)

four features:
"iris" - six eye color palette outputs (brown / blue / green / hazel / grey / purple)
"sclera" - five eye health color palette outputs (healthy / normal / strained / high / insomniac)
"stimuli" - six background color palette outputs (retro / fresh / dark / purple / fire / bnw)
"energy" - five outputs controlling background oscillator frequency and feel (chill / responsive / flow / hyperfocus / delirious)

900 total possible feature combinations
added randomness in iris and background for uniqueness. low but non-zero possibility of minting the same feature set.

metadata.name: Lonely Tree #278
metadata.description:
The bridges have been burned, wrapped in loneliness, and covered in the ashes caused by your fire.

The sound of the wind whispers, longing to carry you away.

With a shattered face, you see others in the distance, they are close, but so far away; the emptiness of this edge is closer than any of them.

But, is it? Looking within isn't hard, it's just a glance and knowing, but it's painfully hard to see.

Disjointed, you tell yourself over and over again that it wasn't for lack of effort.

But, is it? Looking within isn't hard, it's just a glance and knowing, but it's painfully hard to see.

Perhaps you weren't so lonely, perhaps you're not lonely after all.

=== 

CAUTION 

Please be aware that this artwork demands a certain level of CPU power due to the substantial number of elements that need to be rendered on the canvas. Depending on your hardware and the specific features obtained, the rendering process may take anywhere from a few seconds to several minutes to complete. 

=== 

Features

Color Scheme: 
-. Celestial Serenity
-. Serenade of Paleness
-. Tangerine Twilight
-. Verdant Sunset
-. Azure and Citrus Symphony
-. Roseate
-. Serene Whispers
-. Midnight Embers

Cliff Mode:
-. Whispering Abyss
-. Solitude's Edge
-. Eternal Overlook

Waterfall: 
-. Boolean

Signature: 
-. Boolean, if true then a position is selected: Left, Center, Right

Birds' Flock Size: 
-. 1 ("Just a Lonely Bird") to 100

Bird Color
-. Light Fill / Dark Borders
-. Dark Fill / Light Borders
-. Light Fill / Iridescent Borders
-. Dark Fill / Iridescent Borders
-. Iridescent Fill / Dark Borders
-. Crimson Fill / Iridescent Borders
-. Iridescent Fill / Crimson Borders

=== 

Controls
[s] Save image @ 2000x2600 px.
[p] Pause/Play the animation.

===

metadata.name: Manu #226
metadata.description:
Manu
---------------

A collector-led exploration of minimalist imperfect line work.

Outputs are generated from a combination of the minter's address, their choice from one of 50 seeds, and options to adjust how the generated surface is presented.

Palettes are named after native New Zealand birds and range from the subdued to the colorful.

There are no especially rare traits so mint what you love :)

---------------

Controls:
S - Export as png
H - Toggle high resolution

metadata.name: CTT- Circles with Tangent Trace #97
metadata.description:
"Circles with Tangent Trace" is an artistic composition that intricately weaves together geometry and color. Through a meticulous arrangement of circles, each carefully positioned at a specific distance from one another, a remarkable phenomenon emerges. The circles are organized in such a way that a single diagonal line can be drawn, touching each circle at points where the tangent line grazes their edges. This geometric precision creates a mesmerizing effect, as the diagonal trace navigates seamlessly through the vibrant array of colors and forms.

"Circles with Tangent Trace" is not merely a static arrangement; it's a testament to the beauty that emerges from precise mathematical relationships and the artistic expression they can inspire. It encourages viewers to appreciate the balance between mathematical principles and creative intuition, resulting in a captivating and contemplative visual experience.
